title: People Who Die Mysteriously In Their Sleep (Of Natural Causes)(2
description:
Review Summary

This bizarre feature comes from directors David Gaz and Kevin Poore and uses footage from classic films dubbed with new comedic dialogue. In the wake of The Grand Poobah's death, a secret society known as The Caligari has convened to name a successor. An eclectic cast of characters are considered for the job, but will the new Poobah face the same fate as those who came before him? People Who Die Mysteriously in Their Sleep (of Natural Causes) features the voices of Adam Lamas and Darren Meekin. ~ Matthew Tobey, Rovi
